Tonight I made 1/2 of this recipe to serve 2 (yes, I used 1 1/2 eggs). For my 1/2 recipe I used 1/2 red bell and 1/2 green bell peppers, plus about 1 1/2 cups sliced fresh mushrooms, in addition to the required 1/2 cup of green onions. Used 2% milk. Baked it in an 8-1/2 by 4-1/2 inch glass bread loaf pan for about 40 minutes (rotating the dish after the first 20 minutes.) It was VERY GOOD!!! It made 2 generous portions.

